The paper proposes a deep learning approach for generating unambiguous spatial referring expressions in real-world environments, which involves tasks related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also evaluates the proposed method in ambiguous environments, which further supports the relevance to these sub-categories.
